review: This is a pretty cool item. I bought I thought it was cool and different. Is well worth the price and a good thing to have in your guitar case.
I was not a fan of this particular capo. It was good quality and the price was ok but just not my style.
Personally I just love the D'Addario strings. They sute my needs just right for the Takamine acoustic. Great quality and price.
I quess this pic holder may be a pretty good idea but just not something I would use but as I said, It's ok.
Nice strap for the price. Looks nice and quality seems nice. Like the pic holder on front. of the strap.

This is a pretty nice and well built lite weight guitar stand but I have another that is a bit nicer and I paid about the same for both. This particular stand is surely made for a very large jumbo guitar.
If you are a Beatle fan this is such a cute item. Was more than I expected for the price. Nice for collectable or to use.
I love this capo better than any I have seen or used. Great quality and price. You wont go wrong with this capo.
